content: As an AI language model, I don't have personal preferences like humans. However, based on customer reviews and industry analysis, I can tell you that ExpressVPN and NordVPN are two of the most popular VPN services that offer OpenVPN as a protocol option. Both have strong security features, fast servers, a large number of server locations, and user-friendly apps. CyberGhost, PIA, and Surfshark are also solid options that offer OpenVPN and have their own unique features and advantages. Make sure to check their plans, pricing, and customer support before making a decision.
